cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use morie in your research, please cite the language-specific software paper (R: DOI 10.5281/zenodo.20111233; Python: DOI 10.5281/zenodo.20096350). Where applicable to your work, also cite the MRM framework paper (DOI 10.5281/zenodo.20096075), the Hawkes-process methodology paper (DOI 10.5281/zenodo.20102198), and the empirical applications paper (DOI 10.5281/zenodo.20175689)."
title: "morie: Multi-domain Open Research and Inferential Estimation"
authors:
